{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/9230", "repo": "rails", "body": "For what it's worth, this is how NaCl does it:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/jedisct1/libsodium/blob/master/src/libsodium/crypto_verify/32/ref/verify_32.c\r\n\r\n```c\r\nunsigned int differentbits = 0;\r\n#define F(i) differentbits |= x[i] ^ y[i];\r\nF(0)\r\nF(1)\r\nF(2)\r\nF(3)\r\nF(4)\r\nF(5)\r\nF(6)\r\nF(7)\r\nF(8)\r\nF(9)\r\nF(10)\r\nF(11)\r\nF(12)\r\nF(13)\r\nF(14)\r\nF(15)\r\nF(16)\r\nF(17)\r\nF(18)\r\nF(19)\r\nF(20)\r\nF(21)\r\nF(22)\r\nF(23)\r\nF(24)\r\nF(25)\r\nF(26)\r\nF(27)\r\nF(28)\r\nF(29)\r\nF(30)\r\nF(31)\r\nreturn (1 & ((differentbits - 1) >> 8)) - 1;\r\n```", "_id": {"$oid": "5237ebebbd3543c151009c08"}, "issue_id": 9230, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/13340417", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/9230#issuecomment-13340417", "updated_at": "2013-02-09T22:53:02Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tarcieri/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tarcieri/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tarcieri/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tarcieri/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/tarcieri", "login": "tarcieri", "gravatar_id": "4131d2f57a0db2a2b4d9a62bd389fd44", "html_url": "https://github.com/tarcieri", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tarcieri/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tarcieri/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tarcieri/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/4131d2f57a0db2a2b4d9a62bd389fd44?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fbeb22fb694d513edcf5533cf006dfeae.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tarcieri/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 797, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tarcieri/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2013-02-09T22:53:02Z", "id": 13340417, "owner